# Proven Non-Citizen Workers (PNW) Smart Contracts

## **ğŸ”¹ Overview**  
PNW is a blockchain-based payroll and governance system designed for **migrant workers**, ensuring:  
âœ… **Payroll flexibility** â€“ Workers choose **Aleo USDC or Bridged USDC** at any time.  
âœ… **Fair governance** â€“ SubDAOs vote on **worker benefits & fund allocation**.  
âœ… **Employer accountability** â€“ Employers must include **payroll taxes in salary agreements**.  
âœ… **Government compliance** â€“ Labor offices verify work history using **ZPass zero-knowledge proofs**.  

