## **ğŸ”¹ Key Features**  

### **1ï¸âƒ£ Worker Identity (NFT-Based System)**  
- Each worker receives an **NFT identity** that stores:  
  âœ… **Employment history**  
  âœ… **Visa status & expiration**  
  âœ… **Total earnings & trust fund balance**  
- **Government & employers** can verify work history **without exposing private data**.  

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Payroll Processing (Supports Aleo USDC & Bridged USDC)**  
- **Workers choose how they receive payments:**  
  ğŸ”¹ **Aleo USDC** (native Aleo blockchain, gas fees covered by SubDAOs)  
  ğŸ”¹ **Bridged USDC** (EVM-compatible sidechain, workers cover gas fees)  
- **Payroll tax (2%) must be factored into employer salary agreements with SubDAOs.**  
- **ZPass-verified workers receive additional benefits:**  
  âœ… **Priority payroll processing** (faster payments)  
  âœ… **+0.5% APY on unpaid wages in trust fund**  

### **3ï¸âƒ£ Employer-SubDAO Salary Agreements**  
- **Employers must negotiate gross salaries** that **include the 2% payroll tax**.  
- **SubDAOs verify salary agreements before approving payroll.**  
- **Ensures transparency & prevents tax evasion by employers.**  

### **4ï¸âƒ£ SubDAO Governance & Treasury Voting**  
- **Workers participate in SubDAOs**, which control **tax funds collected from payroll**.  
- SubDAOs vote on **fund allocation**, including:  
  âœ… **Worker benefits & emergency relief**  
  âœ… **Education & training programs**  
  âœ… **Infrastructure improvements**  
  âœ… **Investments to grow treasury funds**  

### **5ï¸âƒ£ Worker Protections & Employer Accountability**  
- Workers can **report abusive employers** directly on-chain.  
- If an employer **receives multiple reports**, SubDAOs **vote on penalties** (e.g., contract suspension).  
- Employers who **fail to cover payroll taxes** may face **SubDAO-imposed fines or penalties**.  

### **6ï¸âƒ£ Government API Integration**  
- Approved **government agencies** can **verify work & visa status** via **zero-knowledge proofs**.  
- Helps with **visa renewals, tax compliance, and labor law enforcement**.  

---

## **ğŸ”¹ How PNW Works**  
1ï¸âƒ£ **A migrant worker joins a SubDAO** and receives an **NFT identity**.  
2ï¸âƒ£ **An employer & SubDAO negotiate salary**, ensuring **payroll tax is included**.  
3ï¸âƒ£ **Workers choose their payroll option** (**Aleo USDC or Bridged USDC**).  
4ï¸âƒ£ **Employers process payroll**, with **ZPass workers receiving priority processing**.  
5ï¸âƒ£ **SubDAOs vote on treasury funds**, deciding **how payroll tax is allocated**.  
6ï¸âƒ£ **Governments can verify worker status** to ensure **legal employment compliance**.  

